welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Galena Park! This charming city is known for its rich history, beautiful parks, and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Galena Park has to offer during your stay."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Sugar Land Regional Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Baytown Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Baytown Airport, handling all freight and cargo shipments.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Baytown Airport, exclusively for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights, with 20 gates and various dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: Terminal B

terminals.name: Terminal C
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights, with 31 gates and a variety of dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: Terminal D

terminals.name: Terminal E

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at West Houston Airport serves commercial and private flights, with amenities and services for passengers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal

wifi.note: Passengers can access complimentary WiFi throughout the airport.
